{"tid":1515418,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【邀請連登巴絲】一毫砌畫  現場創作抹出《舊立法會》","createTime":"2019-08-29T06:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:35:35.000Z","uid":143257,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c71bed5947016c96f67cb5b777a2fdc2584d1733","tid":1515418,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"首先，真心多謝各位巴絲一直嘅支持，如果唔係都未必有今次呢個展嘅出現。多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果今晚大家得閒，想邀請你哋一睇黎睇今晚呢個即場創作performance <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 免費入場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kN6OjYv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkN6OjYv.jpg&h=1d9f1849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依加係未見到作品內容住，今日8月29日晚小弟會係中環即場創作。個方法類似之前作品《梅艷芳》。唔明嘅巴打可以睇下面嘅link:<br />\n<br />\n【純金拼圖】小弟用8000個兩毫砌畫 噴出《梅艷芳》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/959761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/959761</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0RVKq7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0RVKq7.jpg&h=e93aeaa0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxz0VxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgxz0VxO.jpg&h=b5825bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實今次展覽都係小弟第一個正式藝術展覽，到時同時會展出之前其他硬幣創作。想邀請各位巴絲聽日黎睇下呢個《立法會》作品嘅即場performance ，同時可以睇下其他作品。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個展覽會為期一個月，如果今日黎唔到嘅巴絲，之後都可以再去睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n展覽細節: <br />\nOpening: 6.30 - 9pm, 8月29日<br />\n（7:10pm 即場創作performance ）<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月29-9月29日 <br />\n（星期一至六11:00-19:00）<br />\n（星期日14:00-17:00）<br />\n<br />\n地點： La Galerie Paris 1839, <br />\nG/F, 74 Hollywood Road, Central, Hong Kong <br />\n（中環PMQ隔離）<br />\n<br />\n另一個多啲 details 嘅post <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513366</a><br />\n<br />\n最後如果大家中意同想睇多d 不如follow 我art.ig 同facebook page<br />\n當支持下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig : gllh_art <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRtiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=aac38e9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art</a><br />\nfb page : Giraffe leung lok hei <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/giraffellh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgiraffellh&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRtiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=bd9933d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/giraffellh</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513366</a>"},{"pid":"b40d64a21f54b30e6cf6cc4f1502d8f25220f022","tid":1515418,"uid":143257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"開左好多個post，唔好意思<br />\n但真係最後召集<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望會見到大家"},{"pid":"6b7cb8772e19f1fc9a5bbd96c9f472173f221718","tid":1515418,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"一定會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29d442ba3a500bf01fa442b088e1533b1b79ad8","tid":1515418,"uid":210405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53eaac4416c346e31d4dd2573e84bbc01ee16af9","tid":1515418,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29d442ba3a500bf01fa442b088e1533b1b79ad8","tid":1515418,"uid":210405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src